步?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "人人都说这是个人情社会，到处是关系户，但是科技在进步，经济在发展，社会在建设，制度在完善。社会总体是前进的。如果说到处都是没有能力的关系户，社会还会进步吗？ 那么，只有两种可能。 第一☝️，要么这些关系户有才能，有实学，是关系户们促进了社会进步，这难道不是选贤举能不避亲？难道不应该提倡吗？难道不是一件好事吗？ 第二，要么这些关系户是少数。绝大多数人都是通过合理的制度选上去的，是这些人促进了社会进步，人类发展。既然是少数，那么怎么又可以说整个社会是人情社会呢？这不是很片面吗？ 由此我们可以得出结论，这个社会不是人情社会，即使是人情社会，也是选贤不避亲的社会。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b45b877f0b098990d4011d15f5b28f2f_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658536920"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIpp6A27+8u8MMEAMaCTEwODYxOTY1MSDSyJmzBjAAOJYBQBxyCTY1ODUzNjkyMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1721970470.761616", "card_id": "Q_661949357", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么主流相声演员不能接受郭德纲?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661949357"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ipp6A27+8u8MMEAMaCTEwOTM3NzY1MSDF1eO0BjAAOC5AHXIJNjYxOTQ5MzU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1800114893787107329", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/662611850", "title": "甘肃出现 1961 年以来最强区域性暴雨", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTgwMDExNDg5Mzc4NzEwNzMyOXITMTgwMDExNDg5Mzc4NzEwNzMyOXgA", "tag": "关注", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}, {"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type"